\[\mathbb{P}\left[|\inf R_{D_{XY}^{Gen}}-\mathbb{E}[\inf R_{D_{XY}^{Gen}}]|>t \right]\leq 2\exp\left(\frac{-2t^{2}}{\sum_{i=1}^{N}c_{i}^{2}}\right)\]

