\[\mathbb{P}\left[|\inf R_{D_{XY}^{Gen}}-\sum_{i=1}^{N}\alpha_{i}\inf R_{inst_{ i}}|>\epsilon\right]\leq 2\exp\left(\frac{-2\epsilon^{2}}{\sum_{i=1}^{N}c_{i}^{2 }}\right)\]

