To evaluate the instance-level prediction performance of deep MIL models, we used the normalized discounted cumulative gain (NDCG@n) and the area under the perturbation curve with random orderings (AOPCR) metrics, as employed by Early et al. [52, 10]. To reliably measure the performance of each model, we repeated the evaluation 10 times and calculated the average performance. AOPCR assesses the interpretability of time-series data by measuring the decrease in model predictions based

